{#
  Multi-agent conference transcript partial.

  Renders the conference transcript chronologically when present, or a
  short opening note when empty. Use this from any conference participant
  or judge prompt that doesn't have a domain-specific wrapper.

  Usage:
      {% include "multi_agent/_transcript.jinja" %}

  Required vars (passed automatically by LLMParticipant / StructuredOutputJudge):
      transcript: chronological text rendering of prior turns; empty string on opening
-#}
{% if transcript %}{{ transcript }}{% else %}_(the discussion has not yet begun — this is the opening turn)_{% endif %}
